{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11876", "repo": "rails", "body": "I don't think we have to add it to Inflector. You can easily add it to one of your initializers\r\n\r\n``` ruby\r\nActiveSupport::Inflector.inflections do |inflect|\r\n  inflect.irregular 'criterion', 'criteria'\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\n(If i am not mistaken, inflector is sort of frozen now for such changes. We can't add all possible examples to Rails) //cc @steveklabnik ", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d080bd3543c151007cd0"}, "issue_id": 11876, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/22613907", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11876#issuecomment-22613907", "updated_at": "2013-08-14T04:07:57Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki", "login": "prathamesh-sonpatki", "gravatar_id": "1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f", "html_url": "https://github.com/prathamesh-sonpatki", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F10a7864f54092aa82b4a41d2f0ec370c.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 621238, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-08-14T04:07:16Z", "id": 22613907, "owner": "rails"}
